parameters = [RangeParameter('x', lower=1, upper=3, parameter_type=
    ParameterType.INT), RangeParameter('y', lower=1, upper=3,
    parameter_type=ParameterType.INT)]
constrained_int_search_space = SearchSpace(parameters=parameters,
    parameter_constraints=[SumConstraint(parameters=parameters,
    is_upper_bound=True, bound=5)])
t = IntToFloat(search_space=constrained_int_search_space,
    observation_features=None, observation_data=None)
self.assertEqual(t.rounding, 'randomized')
observation_features = [ObservationFeatures(parameters={'x': 2.6, 'y': 2.6})]
self.assertTrue(constrained_int_search_space.check_membership(t.
    untransform_observation_features(observation_features=
    observation_features)[0].parameters))
